<h3 class="bold">Video Example(s):</h3>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="hac8hc" data-video-descrip="The trope namer comes from an episode of The Simpsons, titled &amp;quot;King Of The Hill&amp;quot; where McBain is attacked by literal Commie Nazis while delivering UNICEF pennies to children." data-video-title="McBain and the Commie Nazis" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/hac8hc_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/screen_shot_2020_03_30_at_102925_am.png" data-video-trope="Main/CommieNazis" data-video-tropename="Commie Nazis" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="4.96" data-video-rating-count="23" data-video-media-sources="Recap/TheSimpsonsS9E23KingOfTheHill,WesternAnimation/TheSimpsons" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
